msgid "IPSec VPN Server"
msgstr "IPSec VPN 服务器"

msgid "IPSec VPN connectivity using the native built-in VPN Client on iOS or Andriod (IKEv2 PSK & IKEv1 Xauth PSK)<br />IKEv2 Client Mention:<br />Android Client Plsease Set IPsec Identifier With PSK<br />IOS Client Plsease Set Remote ID With PSK"
